data.description: Situated in a quiet neighborhood on the edge of town this four bedroom home is looking for new owners!  Privacy abounds with the large evergreen trees and full privacy fence that circles the yard built for entertaining and enjoyment.  The home has been updated with new flooring, paint, and appliances.  The generously-sized bedrooms and the well-designed layout make this property a truly comfortable place to call home.  The current owners have an assumable FHA loan at 2.875% for qualifying buyers.
